bbcode_enabled = true
text = "Good.

I'm glad you're capable of the immense feat of pushing buttons.

What? Y'wanna medal or something?

Anyway, to more pressing matters.


An unknown alien force has invaded Meridia. Wiped out the USN fleet. Poof! Just like that.

They teleported multiple units aboard this ship, and were busy scrambling my logic cores and searching for any reference to a \"Naaro Kora'thun\" in my databases.


I detected various forms of explosives being used on the surface of Meridia, followed by apparent excavations. I'm going to send you down to find out more about what they are doing.

But first, go collect some ammo and recharge your shields. You're going to need it.
There's an weapons cache downstairs, underneath the bridge. 
Hopefully, the aliens haven't completely ransacked it.


Then, return to this terminal and I'll teleport you down to Meridia.









<Page 1 of 2, press Right Arrow to view page 2> "
